      • addExcludedFromRemoval

        public void addExcludedFromRemoval(KeyableBean toBeExcluded)
        Adds a Keyable bean (which must currently be in the removed set) to the set which will be excluded from removal. This will never exclude beans that are retired.
        Parameters:
        toBeExcluded - The bean to be excluded from retirement

        Returns:
        True if bean is excluded, false otherwise
